          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Sarah Keys Evans Congressional Gold Medal Act&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill provides for the award of a Congressional Gold Medal to Sarah Keys Evans in recognition of her achievements relating to the desegregation of passengers on interstate buses in the 1950s.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
